M-Power Episode 65 Rapid Fire

Did you know Raj Shahani had his first solo exhibition, Caesura/Continuum, which was a celebratory series of the human form captured in the course of executing ballet movements? The sculptures were inspired by dancers in motion and was on display at the Jehangir Art Gallery in Kala Ghoda and then at Gallery Art & Soul in Worli. 

Join us for a fun and interesting Q&A with leading Indian Sculptor and Businessman – Raj Shahani

Get to know more about him on my latest M-Power episode. shahaniraj

On today’s episode I will be sharing with you why Paris should be on your list of destinations when planning a family holiday. Is it an ideal family holiday destination or just an ideal romantic getaway destination for couples? 

This year I got to travel to Paris twice - the first trip in February to celebrate Valentine’s Day with my husband - a much needed getaway for us two. 
 
And the second trip was only 6 weeks later, when we came back with my 15 year older teenage son.

Listen to my full podcast to know how both the trips were completely different yet so much fun! I am also sharing some tips and places to visit as a couple and as a family especially places to eat, shop, spend family time together at and the best touristy sights!
